Package repository

Class PharmacistRepository

java.lang.Object
repository.PharmacistRepository
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPharmacistRepository, IRepository<Pharmacist>
public class PharmacistRepository extends Object implements IPharmacistRepository
An implementation of IRepository that operates on Pharmacist data models. It extends the functionality of a UserRepository by dependency injection to work on Users that are actually Pharmacists.
Since:
2024-11-17
